name: my3D TELEPORT L.A.
description:
MY3D APPS CAN ONLY BE VIEWED WITH THE MY3D VIEWER. VISIT MY3DNOW.COM TO PURCHASE.

With my3D Teleport L.A. you can explore exciting Los Angeles attractions anytime and anywhere…like you’re really there! This unique 360°, 3D interactive virtual tour allows you to experience L.A. from the Santa Monica Pier. You can simply explore or play fun interactive games. Look for other iconic LA locations coming soon. You’ll love your visit to Los Angeles!

COMPATIBLE WITH: iPhone 3GS, 4G; iPod touch 3G (32GB MODEL)& 4G
